{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Convenience function to connect to the [Cancellable](\/\/documentation\/gio\/cancellable\/oncancelled(flags:handler:)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"signal. Also handles the race condition that may happen","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if the cancellable is cancelled right before connecting."}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Cancellable","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Cancellable\/CancellableProtocol-Implementations"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/cancellable\/connect(callback:data:datadestroyfunc:)"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"connect","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"callback"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gclosure.h@T@GCallback","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"GCallback"},{"kind":"text","text":"?, "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"data"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"text":"gpointer","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@gpointer"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil, "},{"text":"dataDestroyFunc","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:gtypes.h@T@GDestroyNotify","text":"GDestroyNotify","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":"? = nil) -> ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:Si","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Int"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"callback","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is called exactly once each time "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"text":" is cancelled,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"either directly at the time of the connect if ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"text":" is already","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"cancelled, or when "},{"code":"cancellable","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" is cancelled in some thread.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In case the cancellable is reset via [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.reset"},{"type":"text","text":"]"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"then the callback can be called again if the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"type":"text","text":" is cancelled and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"if it had not been previously cancelled at the time"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.connect"},{"text":"] was called (e.g. if the connection actually","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"took place, returning a non-zero value)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"code":"dataDestroyFunc","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" will be called when the handler is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"disconnected, or immediately if the cancellable is already","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"cancelled."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"See [Cancellable](\/\/documentation\/gio\/cancellable\/oncancelled(flags:handler:) for details on how to use this."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Since GLib 2.40, the lock protecting "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"cancellable"},{"text":" is not held when","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"callback"},{"text":" is invoked. This lifts a restriction in place for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"earlier GLib versions which now makes it easier to write cleanup","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"code that unconditionally invokes e.g. [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.cancel"},{"type":"text","text":"]."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Note that since 2.82 GLib still holds a lock during the callback but it’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"designed in a way that most of the [class","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Cancellable","type":"reference"},{"text":"] methods can be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"called, including [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.cancel"},{"type":"text","text":"] or"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject.Object.unref"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"There are still some methods that will deadlock (by design) when","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"called from the [signal[Cancellable](\/\/documentation\/gio\/cancellable\/oncancelled(flags:handler:)] callbacks:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.connect"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.disconnect"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Cancellable.reset"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.Cancellable.make_pollfd","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"]","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"Gio.Cancellable.release_fd","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]"}]}]}